The remora example/exercise files are in
~train00/remora_ex.tar (at TACC) or available at github.

Instructions:


    git clone https://github.com/milfeld/remora_ex

    tar -xvf ~train00/remora_ex.tar  # on TACC machines

    cd remora_ex
    

General Instructions:
Read "Instructions" file in each directory.
Do experiments in this order:

         load
         mpi
         memory
         gpu  # GPU required, or course
         io   # does not work on TACC systems
              #    -- due to security restrictions
